title: #13 - Jordan Fisher Reacts to Faze Jarvis Ban & China’s New Gaming Law
itunes:title: #13 - Jordan Fisher Reacts to Faze Jarvis Ban & China’s New Gaming Law
description: On this episode of The CouRage and Nadeshot Show presented by Cash App, CouRage and Nadeshot welcome on quadruple threat, Jordan Fisher. They discuss his Dancing With The Stars victory, Faze Jarvis' lifetime ban from Fortnite, China's new gaming curfew, and more.
